BRITISH AUTHORITIES

31
00:04:40,080 --> 00:04:41,715
HAVE NOW LEARNED
THAT GEORGE QUENNELL

32
00:04:41,749 --> 00:04:42,783
AND ANGUS PETHERBRIDGE,

33
00:04:42,816 --> 00:04:47,455
THE TWO DIPLOMATS WHO
FLED ENGLAND ON MAY 25TH, 1951

34
