HAD BEEN SOVIET SPIES

36
00:04:51,359 --> 00:04:53,661
SINCE THEIR RECRUITMENT
AT CAMBRIDGE UNIVERSITY.

37
00:04:53,694 --> 00:04:56,764
THE LENGTH OF THEIR DECEPTION
