64
00:06:09,603 --> 00:06:12,673
LEO,
THIS IS SALLY TYLER.

65
00:06:12,706 --> 00:06:13,574
PLEASED TO MEET YOU, SALLY.

66
00:06:13,607 --> 00:06:14,542
AND YOU, LEO.

67
